{"tid":2370974,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"見有巴打問電影 我又試吓問玩具 有無8，90後嘅巴絲入嚟幫吓","createTime":"2021-01-18T12:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T13:24:37.000Z","uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"937c4e60599a461c2a013fae67a01ef1e1e6932f","tid":2370974,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:16:39.000Z","msg":"記得細個萬寧有賣一個叫整蠱爐嘅玩具 個爐要插電嘅 係放個鐵鑄嘅鐵板入個爐燒 要放啲汁液落個鐵板度 之後燒出嚟會變咗軟der der 嘅軟膠 有昆蟲 恐龍之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用嚟嚇人 唔知係咪又係得我一個記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定得我一個玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外仲有一隻都係賣寧有賣嘅 係同fd一齊玩嘅 機械人 個機械人用遙控控制佢嘅 不斷自轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拎住個武器打中對方個機械人嘅盾牌，對方隻機械人就會訓低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef3807bd7d4fd20aa9b6751dc421116afbeda7a","tid":2370974,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de07207266caa18d6b1338ea06b8705c22749f04","tid":2370974,"uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T12:43:43.000Z","msg":"你google整蠱爐咪有人講過<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXfOWMgWYLk&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPXfOWMgWYLk%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=8edda45a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXfOWMgWYLk&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n第4個"},{"pid":"02e7c7571dcdd33f03a9f1ca31bfea711d7cc343","tid":2370974,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de07207266caa18d6b1338ea06b8705c22749f04","tid":2370974,"uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r